{"tid":2396622,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實瞓覺唔需要枕頭?","createTime":"2021-02-05T17:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T03:32:15.000Z","uid":300918,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0fd9e1354df562a5af1e70a9c6fd6682ff8d4e0b","tid":2396622,"uid":300918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:46:08.000Z","msg":"正確睡姿應該係企直轉90&deg;瞓<br />\n咁有舊枕頭頂住咪即係駝背<br />\n枕頭呢樣野根本就係由資本家<br />\n透過廣告宣傳洗腦誕生既產物<br />\n仲要越出越多花款<br />\n咩記憶海綿<br />\n智能枕頭啊<br />\n目的就係從中穫利<br />\n同時令你睡姿唔正確瞓得唔好<br />\n起身冇精神<br />\n自然返工返學都冇曬動力<br />\n冇辦法上進就永遠困喺社會底層<br />\n資本家既地位亦得以鞏固<br />\n簡直係馴化奴隸既必需品<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbb25fa3731f65ede5d80245952c8c56732749e","tid":2396622,"uid":60393,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:47:47.000Z","msg":"枕頭係俾你攬住"},{"pid":"1a422cd1f282fd9ec64feb77dc80ffdbdef8251e","tid":2396622,"uid":142854,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:49:13.000Z","msg":"我訓教用開石頭<br />\n久而久之個後腦粒左入去<br />\n而家做左社會賢達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個月拎傷殘津貼"},{"pid":"68a27b349079f22db520f932d7ce5120b3c11bd9","tid":2396622,"uid":300918,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccbb25fa3731f65ede5d80245952c8c56732749e","tid":2396622,"uid":60393,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:47:47.000Z","msg":"枕頭係俾你攬住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:50:07.000Z","msg":"攬住你得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fbb5a697ad017bc0a002a9186e676fb9c3b240c","tid":2396622,"uid":200529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:50:52.000Z","msg":"I don't use<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b85086236cd5b136aab88559e5cb803353f8b24","tid":2396622,"uid":304281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:51:25.000Z","msg":"用嚟打側訓<img src